Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,默默地为你着想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是悄悄藏在你看不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以平时毫无察觉地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一旦回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你着想的那个人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会朦胧地浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果激烈地浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们就称之为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 我今天做了烤奶油马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想让爸爸妈妈吃到好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坑坑洼洼的 样子糟糕得不好意思拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 一点也不会糟糕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为里面充满了小爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为蓝华今天去参加公司员工的旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只有我跟爱丽丝两个人一起练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的声音好好听 好好听哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为领航员最重要的是划船的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 难道你心情不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让比你年长的我来听你倾诉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事都不要客气 告诉姐姐吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…我的左手太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近发觉我的左手非常笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟右手比 既无法拿好筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没办法写出端正的字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那个…有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我正在惩罚左手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太依赖右手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都把所有事情交给右手做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把这当作理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有想办法解决过这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近养了一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:19.74,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 想要守护的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是领航员协会中最顶尖的橙色行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是宿舍严禁养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系吗？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手特训？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它嘛嘛地叫 就取名为小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:03:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天前它被丢弃在路边时 被我捡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你一个很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想找蓝华前辈商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不巧她去公司员工的旅行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才找了灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回我们公司里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给亚利亚社长圆不隆咚的肚子造成大危机的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛 别叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不是奇怪的人…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是跟我同寝室的雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说进房间前要敲门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才被你吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你了 我是亚利亚公司的水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一位是我们公司的亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？爱丽丝 雅典娜前辈是不是长得跟刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一位唱着美妙歌声的人有一点像？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就是她本人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三大精灵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就属雅典娜前辈的Canzone最为有名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}Canzone：意大利语「歌」的意思 这里特指船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人就是传说中的雅典娜前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈要住下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前请先换上本公司的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那样超级显眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 小嘛会不会被雅典娜前辈发现呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止都还能应付过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为雅典娜前辈超级喜欢发呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇…好像豪华餐厅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日三餐大都是在这里解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 这杯水是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没发觉是雅典娜前辈帮她拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈又把全部的奶精放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看雅典娜前辈那样 她可是个很笨拙的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:08:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常在走廊上跌倒 还经常把饮料打翻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是连最重要的事情都会忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打电话的时候还会自己不小心把电话挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说她有多笨拙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概跟我的左手差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 不可以这样说自己的前辈啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两个都完全不在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚会跟亚利亚社长在您宿舍暂住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是爱找麻烦 这时候就要用左手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 请您先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛 吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗？小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小嘛的事告诉雅典娜前辈也没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 因为就算是前辈也改不了规定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你打算把它就这么藏着养吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要这么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前 橙色行星的社长去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到小嘛就会想起它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位社长跟小嘛很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一点也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 哎呀… 前辈洗得舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说应该已经暴露了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的猜拳游戏…当然输的都是左手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在黑漆漆的地方会不会寂寞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…败露了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈的歌唱得真是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 左手可能没你想的那么笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈今天公司休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在衣橱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去上学了 前辈请慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这能持续到什么时候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}这就是移居的一大原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}好 正如上次课堂上所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}大规模的AQUA移居计划其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}已经是五十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}在那之前积累了无数次的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为昨天那件事 可能已经有人发现小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手可能没你想的那么笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手总是在背后默默地支持着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是今天起跟您同室的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝·卡罗尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛…小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛它…小嘛它…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去哪了呢？小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是被雅典娜前辈发现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后告诉公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…不能把事情往坏的地方想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到猫了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到爱丽丝的房间传来猫的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以打开了衣橱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它就逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…不是雅典娜前辈丢掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈早就察觉到小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是为了掩饰小嘛的哭声才特意唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…比左手还要没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小嘛都保护不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你回来 小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛也显得很安心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对小嘛而言 爱丽丝也是重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道您刚才唱歌是为了找小嘛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也是为了掩饰小嘛的哭声吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都没察觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚住进宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为害怕 睡不着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时你也是这样唱着歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是…还有 在我失眠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也总是像这样 是为我而唱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为歌声…是要传达给别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跟公司商量过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗？虽然太小不易察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这孩子确实拥有蓝色的眼睛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子将成为橙色行星的新社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色眼睛的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手…是超级伟大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在开始要练习向左手道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 我把烤奶油马铃薯忘在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什么时候被爸爸吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了一张字条…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写着「味道还可以 我期待你下次的作品」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便吃人家的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟说「还可以」 这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很过分对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也因此从低落中走了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心变得很温暖 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 可能我们大家不知何时起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在被别人默默支持着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人无法察觉地 默默地…悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能坐上晃前辈的凤尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.98,0:24:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么高兴也只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 美好的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.41,0:24:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:21.80,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:30.97,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:40.58,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:51.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:59.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:09.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:18.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:29.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:39.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.82,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:21.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}轻拂面颊的 温柔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:30.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:40.58,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:51.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:59.60,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:09.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:18.86,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:29.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:39.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.82,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}水之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:49.19,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:56.76,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:23:00.45,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:08.46,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.77,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:19.39,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:27.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:31.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:39.15,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:44.94,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:53.36,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:59.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:49.19,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不变的景色 倒映在水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:56.76,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在缓缓流逝的时光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:23:00.45,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不断变化的季节中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:08.46,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}寻觅到 那不变的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.77,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}听 那幸福的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:19.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}像这样 一直 满溢于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:27.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的梦想 都将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:31.24,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 总会越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:39.15,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨后的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:44.94,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 总会展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:53.36,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的爱意 定会见到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:59.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常怀爱意 定能越过彩虹
